      "text": "Legend:\n  Red border = Grid (2×2 blocks)\n  Blue area  = Block (4×4 threads each)\n  Green cell = Thread (x,y) within block\n\nTotal threads: 2×2 × 4×4 = 64\nCovers matrix up to 8×8",
